{"rule_id": "b15cd779-09a8-4f1d-82de-1de9f937f8dd", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "prohibited_products", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁售危险与违法商品", "summary": "卖家不得上架枪支、烟酒、爆炸物、危险化学品、成人内容等非法、不安全或受管制商品。", "content": "## 禁售/受限商品\n- 严禁上架：枪支弹药、烟草、酒精、爆炸品、危险化学/易燃易爆材料、武器、成人内容等。\n- 凡属违法、不安全或受社会监管的品类一律禁止。\n- 部分品类为受限商品，需具备相应资质或完全禁止。\n- 违规商品将被下架，并触发对店铺的处罚（详见处罚分级）。\n\n注：完整禁售清单以官方支持页与卖家协议为准。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/support/c2/prohibited-products-f-326.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["prohibited", "safety", "compliance"]}
{"rule_id": "cbbe8518-9930-49a3-a78e-3997ef43d37f", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "penalties", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "禁售违规三级处罚机制", "summary": "卖家违反禁售政策按严重程度分三级处罚，从下架商品到永久封店递进。", "content": "## 违规处罚分级（待核验）\n- **一级**：较轻违规。卖家须下架并停售涉事商品，撤下平台店铺广告。\n- **二级**：中度违规。涉事商品下架/禁售、撤广告，可能须清理旧 listing 且不得新增上架。\n- **三级**：永久封禁，限制乃至关停店铺，不得再上架新品。\n\n注：分级名称与触发条件为 WebSearch 二手概括，具体阈值待以官方卖家协议核验。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["penalty", "enforcement", "prohibited"]}
{"rule_id": "1d843d9f-0b91-47e7-b508-7ab436f9cdd2", "platform": "temu", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止侵犯知识产权", "summary": "卖家上架前须同意不侵犯任何版权、商标、专利等知识产权，违者商品下架。", "content": "## 知识产权红线\n- 受保护类型：版权、商标、专利及法律规定的其他知识产权。\n- 卖家不得在商品、包装、图片或描述中未经授权使用他人版权作品、商标或专利。\n- 上架前须同意明确禁止 IP 侵权的政策。\n- 收到合规的侵权报告后，Temu 将下架被举报材料并对责任方采取相应措施。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/intellectual-property-policy.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["ip", "trademark", "copyright", "patent"]}
{"rule_id": "c2742e35-810d-41fd-847f-d308a8dbbcb3", "platform": "temu", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "penalty", "title": "重复侵权者终止合作", "summary": "Temu 对重复侵权的卖家在适当情形下予以终止；恶意虚假举报亦担责。", "content": "## 重复侵权与滥用举报\n- Temu 在适当情形下**终止重复侵权者**的合作/账户。\n- 提交虚假或失实的侵权通知须承担损害赔偿责任，多次失实举报可能丧失举报权限。\n- 平台称已将 99%+ 的下架请求在 3 个工作日内处理，多数 24 小时内完成。\n\n注：99% 处理时效为官方宣传口径，作业绩参考。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/intellectual-property-policy.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": ["1d843d9f-0b91-47e7-b508-7ab436f9cdd2"], "tags": ["ip", "repeat-infringer", "penalty"]}
{"rule_id": "397c7bed-7187-47d2-8115-757e7de8a938", "platform": "temu", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "intellectual_property", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "知识产权侵权举报流程", "summary": "权利人或授权代理可经官方 IP 门户提交权属证明与初步侵权证据发起下架。", "content": "## IP 举报流程\n- 举报人须为权利人本人，或经权利人授权的代理。\n- 须通过 Temu 专设的 IP 投诉在线门户提交：权属证明、权利人信息、初步侵权证据。\n- 材料合规后，Temu 会移除被指侵权的商品。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/support/c3/what-is--intellectual-property--f-60-s-178.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": ["1d843d9f-0b91-47e7-b508-7ab436f9cdd2"], "tags": ["ip", "report", "process"]}
{"rule_id": "48feb08e-823f-4f5e-ab38-03a44874793d", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "退货时间窗与寄回时限", "summary": "多数商品自购买起 90 天内可退；提交退货申请后须 14 天内寄回。", "content": "## 退货时间窗\n- 多数商品：自购买之日起 **90 天**内可申请退货退款。\n- 电子产品退货窗较短，常见 45/60/90 天，依卖家而定。\n- 买家提交退货申请后，须在 **14 天**内将退货包裹寄出。\n- 卖家可额外指定某些商品为不可退。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/return-and-refund-policy.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["returns", "refund", "consumer"]}
{"rule_id": "c5e803f0-a44b-4054-8f69-6f5cd0bc77dd", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "退货运费规则", "summary": "同一订单首次退货免运费，第二次及以后退货收取 $7.99（加税）运费。", "content": "## 退货运费\n- 90 天窗口内，**同一订单首次退货免运费**。\n- 同一订单第二次及之后的退款，每次收取 **$7.99 + 税** 退货运费。\n- 超大件或偏远地区退货需先行垫付运费，经检验通过后再申请报销。\n- 原始运费一般不予退还，除非问题由 Temu 或卖家造成。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/return-and-refund-policy.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": ["48feb08e-823f-4f5e-ab38-03a44874793d"], "tags": ["returns", "shipping-fee"]}
{"rule_id": "c86a6111-0805-4714-a446-197c799ab580", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "不可退货商品范围", "summary": "已穿洗/去标的服饰、内衣泳衣、食品杂货、定制品、赠品等通常不可退。", "content": "## 不可退商品\n- 已穿、已洗、已损或去除吊牌/卫生贴的服饰（含内衣、袜子、泳衣）。\n- 食品杂货、部分健康/个护用品。\n- 定制商品、促销品、免费赠品。\n- 卖家可在上述基础上指定额外的不可退商品。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/support/c3/what-is--return--f-50-s-114.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": ["48feb08e-823f-4f5e-ab38-03a44874793d"], "tags": ["returns", "non-returnable"]}
{"rule_id": "f5cc379f-3236-408a-b991-31c1bd1b164f", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "退款检验与处理时效", "summary": "退货经质检通过后退款，通常 5-14 个工作日到账，最长可达 30 天。", "content": "## 退款处理\n- 退货收到并通过**质量检验**后才会处理退款。\n- 处理时效通常为收货检验后 5-14 个工作日，Temu 提示最长可达 30 天。\n- 若退回商品为使用/损坏、缺件、或因退货包装不当受损（非 Temu/卖家原因），退款将相应扣减以补偿价值损失。\n- 买家可选更快的 Temu 信用额度退款。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/return-and-refund-policy.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": ["48feb08e-823f-4f5e-ab38-03a44874793d"], "tags": ["after-sales", "refund", "inspection"]}
{"rule_id": "29288d48-3707-406b-ab97-731132e7253a", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "fee", "title": "延迟送达补偿", "summary": "标准运输延迟补偿 $5 信用、快递运输延迟补偿 $13 信用。", "content": "## 延迟送达补偿（待核验）\n- 标准运输延迟：向买家补偿约 **$5 信用**。\n- 快递运输延迟：补偿约 **$13 信用**。\n- 延迟送达会影响卖家的履约表现与搜索排名。\n\n注：补偿金额为二手概括，且补偿成本是否由卖家承担需以官方卖家政策核验。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/support/c3/what-is-late-delivery--f-48-s-1633.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["logistics", "late-delivery", "compensation"]}
{"rule_id": "4209f8c3-7cfa-4c98-882f-3a7c2c5504be", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "发货时效要求", "summary": "卖家须在 1-2 个工作日内发货；JIT 模式入仓须在约 72 小时内完成。", "content": "## 发货时效\n- Temu 期望卖家在 **1-2 个工作日**内发货，延迟会拉低履约评分与搜索排名。\n- JIT（接单后入仓）模式：商品须在约 **72 小时**内送达仓库，否则面临处罚。\n- 半托管/本土店鼓励使用 Temu 美国仓或 3PL 仓以缩短时效。\n\n注：具体小时数为二手概括，待以官方卖家后台规则核验。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["logistics", "fulfillment", "semi-managed", "JIT"]}
{"rule_id": "8d4e504a-9d81-4e16-8df2-c4a9c857b97d", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "包装与保护要求", "summary": "须用安全、加固包装保护易碎品；服饰配件须用透明拉链袋。", "content": "## 包装要求（待核验）\n- 使用低调、安全的包装，易碎品须加缓冲保护。\n- 服装与配件须使用透明拉链袋包装。\n- 包装不合规可能触发履约处罚/扣款。\n\n注：包装规格为综合性二手概括，具体标准待以官方卖家后台核验。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["logistics", "packaging"]}
{"rule_id": "471b255d-51b3-45c3-9b5a-0d2a9bbe9dc2", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "类目驱动的商品数据要求", "summary": "上架须按叶子类目填全属性，标题、描述、图片、SKU、规格、价格等结构化数据齐备。", "content": "## 商品数据要求\n- Temu 采用类目驱动的数据模型，所需属性取决于所选类目。\n- 类目须选到**叶子层级（最具体级别）**。\n- 必填/结构化数据：标题、商品描述、图片、SKU、规格、尺寸/尺码、价格。\n- 推荐字段虽非发布必填，但影响曝光，建议视为必填逐条补全。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["listing", "product-data", "category"]}
{"rule_id": "214354b4-071c-42e9-931d-0f6917e8ebb6", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "商品图片与标题规范", "summary": "主图须白底，可加最多 10 张副图；标题须含关键词且控制在 120 字符内。", "content": "## 图文规范（待核验）\n- **主图须白底**（强制）。\n- 副图最多 10 张，含场景图、细节特写、服饰尺码图、开箱内容图。\n- 标题以关键词为主，控制在约 **120 字符**以内。\n- 描述须含尺寸、材质、兼容性、保养说明等。\n\n注：字符数与图片张数为二手概括，待以官方上架规范核验。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": ["471b255d-51b3-45c3-9b5a-0d2a9bbe9dc2"], "tags": ["listing", "images", "title"]}
{"rule_id": "25f10f15-fcf0-435e-afdf-51d0465b41c7", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "prohibition", "title": "禁止违规上架行为", "summary": "禁止重复铺货、使用未经核实的图片、以及操纵评论。", "content": "## 禁止的上架行为\n- 不得重复上架同款商品（重复铺货）。\n- 不得使用未经核实/盗用的商品图片。\n- 不得操纵、刷写商品评论。\n\n违规会影响店铺表现并可能触发处罚。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/terms-of-use.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": ["471b255d-51b3-45c3-9b5a-0d2a9bbe9dc2"], "tags": ["listing", "anti-abuse", "reviews"]}
{"rule_id": "b80169af-0577-4e13-85d1-b95f3252c226", "platform": "temu", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "入驻资质与证件要求", "summary": "入驻须提交营业执照、法人/店长身份证件、品牌资质、收款账户及供货能力证明。", "content": "## 入驻资质\n- 营业执照（注册）。\n- 法人代表与店铺管理者的有效政府身份证件（护照/驾照等）。\n- 品牌资质证明：商标、授权书等。\n- 用于打款的银行账户信息已验证。\n- 制造/供货能力证明，必要时提供仓储或本土物流合作证明。\n- 所有证件有效期须在申请时距到期至少 1 年。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["onboarding", "qualification", "business-license"]}
{"rule_id": "e5dbfb02-10cd-46da-9833-8f3c00d4fc0c", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "店铺类型与入驻审核", "summary": "卖家须选择店铺类型（旗舰/专营/授权零售等）并选定主营类目，审核约 3-7 个工作日。", "content": "## 店铺类型与审核\n- 须选择业务类型与店铺类型：旗舰店、类目旗舰店、专营店、授权零售店等。\n- 美国卖家可在 Temu 卖家中心直接注册，无需邀请码。\n- 提交资质表后，约 **3-7 个工作日**收到审核结果（邮件 + 短信通知）。\n\n注：审核时长为二手概括，以官方通知为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": ["b80169af-0577-4e13-85d1-b95f3252c226"], "tags": ["onboarding", "store-type", "US"]}
