{"rule_id": "6d41077a-e2c5-4f3d-88e5-a9d5aaa47517", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "产品安全合规与检测", "summary": "Temu 将化学检测纳入例行合规审核，玩具与电池类商品转向全型号检测。", "content": "## 产品安全合规（待核验）\n- 化学检测已纳入 Temu 例行合规审核。\n- 检测报告须完整，覆盖全部检测点位、材料与颜色变体。\n- 玩具与电池供电类商品转向**全型号检测**，而非抽样检测，合规成本上升。\n- CE 认证类商品须在机体永久标注制造商名称与地址。\n\n注：检测口径为二手概括，具体清单/标准以官方合规要求为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["compliance", "product-safety", "testing"]}
{"rule_id": "9aa40644-204f-48bc-bb49-ba2c80f83b24", "platform": "temu", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "tax_compliance", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "欧盟 EPR 与 VAT 合规", "summary": "在德法西奥等国销售须完成 EPR 注册申报与缴费，并按规定登记缴纳 VAT。", "content": "## EPR / VAT（待核验，主要适用欧盟）\n- **EPR**：Temu 在德国、法国、西班牙、奥地利等强制要求 EPR 合规，涵盖包装法、WEEE、电池指令。卖家须完成注册、申报与环境费缴纳；不合规可致扣款、下架或冻结资金。\n- **VAT**：在 EU 任一国存货须注册缴纳 VAT；跨境包裹经 IOSS 缴 VAT。英国 VAT 注册门槛为滚动 12 个月内 £90,000。\n\n注：此条主要适用欧盟/英国站点，金额阈值为二手概括，以各国官方规定为准。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://seller.temu.com/policy-page.html?type=10", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "low", "related_rule_ids": ["6d41077a-e2c5-4f3d-88e5-a9d5aaa47517"], "tags": ["tax", "vat", "epr", "eu"]}
{"rule_id": "76e5ca79-684e-42fb-bc03-8c18af56c970", "platform": "temu", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "遵守平台使用条款", "summary": "卖家须遵守 Temu 使用条款，禁止欺诈、滥用与违反平台规则的行为。", "content": "## 平台使用条款\n- 卖家与用户须遵守 Temu《使用条款》对账户行为的总体约定。\n- 禁止欺诈、操纵、滥用平台机制及任何违反平台规则的行为。\n- 违反条款可导致账户限制或终止。\n\n注：具体条款以官方使用条款全文为准。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/terms-of-use.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["account-health", "terms", "compliance"]}
{"rule_id": "8ad15b09-bb5e-4005-bb3b-8085e636c0da", "platform": "temu", "site": "US", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "requirement", "title": "卖家信息披露义务（INFORM Act）", "summary": "作为市场平台，Temu 须依美国 INFORM Consumers Act 披露第三方卖家信息并提供举报机制。", "content": "## 卖家信息披露（INFORM Consumers Act）\n- 美国 INFORM Consumers Act 要求市场平台收集、核验并披露高频第三方卖家的身份与联系信息。\n- 须向消费者提供举报可疑卖家的机制。\n- 2025 年 FTC 以未履行该披露义务为由对 Temu 处以 $2,000,000 民事罚款（首例 INFORM Act 执法）。\n\n对卖家影响：需配合提供并核验真实身份/联系信息以满足平台披露要求。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://www.temu.com/terms-of-use.html", "version": "2026.06.21-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-21", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "medium", "related_rule_ids": ["76e5ca79-684e-42fb-bc03-8c18af56c970"], "tags": ["after-sales", "inform-act", "disclosure", "us-law"]}
